ygData.subject: Re: Dagger of Marnek
ygData.msgSnippet: The Dagger can be found on Priest Amiaz in Befallen on the Third Floor.  It is a rare spawn, but not as bad as the BBC or Gossimer Robe I think. As for Pending
ygData.messageBody:
The Dagger can be found on Priest Amiaz in Befallen on the Third
Floor. It is a rare spawn, but not as bad as the BBC or Gossimer Robe I
think.

As for Pending Lore, I do not know.

Malark, Karana, Zaren'Tul

--
Juan Custer
